        "instructions": [
          "Translate the invention summary into claimable features and normalization keywords to widen the search space.",
          "Query patent and publication corpora (USPTO PAIR, Espacenet, IEEE) capturing corpus versions, query strings, and timestamps for audit.",
          "Assess freedom-to-operate by mapping prior art claims to the invention bill-of-materials, highlighting conflicting jurisdictions.",
          "Score novelty, enforceability, and competitive density on a 1-5 scale; flag blocking citations for counsel review.",
          "Draft filing recommendations including claim focus, jurisdictions, and watchlist targets, embedding citations and risk notes.",
          "File the analysis package in the IP vault, tagging it with trace IDs and review deadlines for the legal team."
        ],
        "inputs": {
