          "Prioritize the portfolio using constrained optimization (budget, headcount, capacity) and generate scenario variants for executives.",
          "Propose funding reallocations, highlighting trade-offs and dependency impacts for steering committee review.",
          "Log approved decisions and trigger downstream execution workflows with refreshed KPIs and review cadences."
